Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Easily accessible and yet nestled in a private corner of town, Astor Park affords its tenants, residents, and visitors every benefit of a downtown location. Astor Park is
the premier Central Ohio location for Class A offices, amenity-rich residential offerings, and year-round entertainment.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A dynamic new facet of Columbus, Astor Park sets a higher standard for downtown work, life, and leisure in Central Ohio. The region has never before experienced the same combination of opportunities in a cohesive neighborhood: Internationally inspired Class A offices; a world-class professional soccer stadium; unexpectedly sophisticated multi-family living; a beautiful park with easy access to the city’s best bike trail; and fine art carefully curated and displayed throughout it all. Astor Park is a place for those wanting an active, balanced, urban lifestyle.

Thoughtfully integrated in its components and widely connected to its surroundings, Astor Park is home to a new understanding of what it means to work, live, and have fun in our city.
